<h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
<p>The Center for Equal Opportunity is a key player in the conservative movement, advocating for colorblind public policies and equal treatment under the law. While its mission aligns with conservative values, its opposition to affirmative action and ties to the Trump administration warrant close scrutiny. CEOâ€™s continued influence on national policy and its role in shaping the future political landscape will be important to monitor.</p>

